Best known for his highly energetic live performances and next-level mixing abiliites the selektor masterfully blends the sounds of deep dubstep, wonkier/bouncier styles, and most recently he has been dabbling in the grime scene as well depending on his crowd and setting! 

Dating back to some of his earliest live performances in 2012, the young talent has proved that he has what it takes to get crowds moving and skankin' out and leaves a lasting impression on his audience- regardless of his time slot! 

Drawing influence from artists such as Requake, P0gman, Badklaat, Jakes & Subfiltronik, Sektah's hard-hitting style captures crowds and takes them on an adrenaline-fueled journey that doesn't let go until the very end!

Aside from Sub.mission, Sektah is also a member of the artist collective 'Villainz Dubstep,' based out of Houston, Texas.

Driven by his profound passion and knowledge for bass music, Sektah is emerging as one of the hottest talents to grace the electronic music scene in Colorado and out-of-state bookings are on the upcoming horizon for the young talent!
